Package: RHigh
Title: RHigh is an R Package to Facilitate High School Statistics Education
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Lomuscio", , "lomuscio.michael@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: RHigh is a user-friendly R package designed to empower high school statistics teachers to use R with their students. It provides a set of tools that closely mimic those commonly found on scientific calculators, facilitating an easier transition to utilizing R in the classroom. The package aims to make statistical analysis more accessible and engaging for high school students, promoting a deeper understanding of statistical concepts and their authentic applications.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    tibble, 
    dplyr,
    stats
  
